[[File:Sandbuzzer-aotc.png|thumb|Two sand-buzzers at the [[Lars homestead/Legends|Lars homestead]] with [[Owen Lars/Legends|Owen Lars]]' [[Zephyr-G swoop/Legends|Zephyr-G swoop]] between them.]]
The '''sand-buzzer''' was a security device that emitted an electronic field to drive away small burrowing pest animals, such as [[Scurrier/Legends|scurriers]].

Commonly employed on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], many [[Moisture farm/Legends|moisture farms]] had sand-buzzers surrounding the homestead to damage to the property, particularly the sunken walls of the homestead courtyards.

